{"tid":1765302,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中共如何滲透其他政府/組織?","createTime":"2019-12-01T18:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T01:08:04.000Z","uid":292644,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"99e5b92a22c148cb053017e318e7655840e2e310","tid":1765302,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非巴絲請幫手研究呢份野<br />\n呢份野人地做左好耐,講大陸政府點滲透.要抗爭落去冇理由唔睇<br />\n新區議員更加要睇,識英文有學歷既巴絲麻煩幫下大家解讀<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bannedbook.org/bnews/zh-tw/cbnews/20190414/1113447.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bannedbook.org%2Fbnews%2Fzh-tw%2Fcbnews%2F20190414%2F1113447.html&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0TcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=c6821c4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bannedbook.org/bnews/zh-tw/cbnews/20190414/1113447.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;紐西蘭著名中國問題專家布萊迪針對最近紐西蘭社會對於中共滲透問題的強烈關注在推特上發文說：&ldquo;對於像紐西蘭這樣的開放社會，很難抵禦外國的政治干預。重新再看我在2017年發表的文章，反思我們所面臨的挑戰；同時我也在思考，自從我寫這篇文章以來我們已經走到了哪一步。&rdquo;（布萊迪教授提供）&quot;<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wilsoncenter.org/article/magic-weapons-chinas-political-influence-activities-under-xi-jinping\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wilsoncenter.org%2Farticle%2Fmagic-weapons-chinas-political-influence-activities-under-xi-jinping&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0TcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=b2da8064\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wilsoncenter.org/article/magic-weapons-chinas-political-influence-activities-under-xi-jinping</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wilsoncenter.org/sites/default/files/for_website_magicweaponsanne-mariesbradyseptember2017.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wilsoncenter.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Ffor_website_magicweaponsanne-mariesbradyseptember2017.pdf&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0TcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=758054d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wilsoncenter.org/sites/default/files/for_website_magicweaponsanne-mariesbradyseptember2017.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"d283f27957c25979af1334757a045e14f7d77568","tid":1765302,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T19:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac69baf2df3881a96709473c50c323e3933092e0","tid":1765302,"uid":170014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T19:33:11.000Z","msg":"128 死線 129大三罷 同我推上去熱門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1765338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1765338</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"030e538c40b13db4d661741f761b20ef5fefdc14","tid":1765302,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T19:42:45.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"31ac6915f05b4a88bb7bbfd17c0b269091c6c925","tid":1765302,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T19:46:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2f0aa50182d9b19813742c58946a026db961f36","tid":1765302,"uid":52339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T19:56:28.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"d8210ac4353bfb909e618b1accc777ed5e35042b","tid":1765302,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:08:04.000Z","msg":"Tui"}]}